name: Stink Coin
description: Stink Coin is a meme coin launched on the Pump.fun platform, characterized by its humorous theme centered around the concept of 'stink'. Post its initial bonding phase, it transitioned into a community-managed project after the original developer's departure. Stink Coin embodies the spirit of humor within the meme coin ecosystem, serving as a token for community interaction with no specific utility beyond its speculative nature and as a testament to community spirit.
